00:00:24.357 --> 00:00:26.401 position:50% align:center
Now, now. What's done is done,

00:00:26.484 --> 00:00:29.404 position:50% align:center
and besides, we should
be happy the term's over!

00:00:29.487 --> 00:00:31.239 position:50% align:center
